      "content": "i dont think a conversation is gonna change anything. it’s just a cycle of them getting more tired and me feeling more guilty. i keep thinking... if i wasn't a factor anymore, they could finally just breathe. they could live their own lives without this constant worry. does it ever make sense to just... stop? to just let go so they can have their peace back?",
